  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nThe HTTP dispatcher instantiation does not forward the query string (search parameter) to `undici`. This results in malfunction when there's relevant information (api key, jwt token, etc.) on the query string. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/main/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/core/providers/http.ts#L186-L196\r\n\r\nSupport for query params in Undici was added here, and is already loaded with latest hardhat. \r\nhttps://github.com/nodejs/undici/issues/1448\r\n\r\n\r\n\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
